Package assignments

The assignments package contains the necessary files for Assignments, Assignment Submissions, Assignment Solutions, Courses, and Grading.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Assignment
    Assignment is a set of files representing a method of evaluation for a course.
    AssignmentSolution
    A solution set for a particular Assignment.
    AssignmentSubmission
    A set of answers created by a Student for a particular Assignment and submitted for evaluation.
    Comments
    Comments that can optionally be submitted with the Grade evaluation of an Assignment Submission.
    Course
    A semester-specific offering of a course.
    Grade
    A grade given to a particular Assignment Submission.
    SubmissionReceipt
    A submission confirmation to be returned to the client when an AssignmentSubmission is submitted.

Package assignments Description

The assignments package contains the necessary files for Assignments, Assignment Submissions, Assignment Solutions, Courses, and Grading.
